{"tid":2181302,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［突發］警方消息指：831將會派出國安人員監察悼念活動！","createTime":"2020-08-30T13:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T19:01:06.000Z","uid":219007,"like":84,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"546524425173d5e5b2e6c58bc99d7c3d17e5d74b","tid":2181302,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:23:15.000Z","msg":"明天是太子站8.31事件一周年。一直向政府和警方追究事件的油尖旺民主派區議員，在警方日前來信「懇請」停止所有集會下，明日傍晚將如常在太子站外以「兩人一更」的方式替市民獻花，再於翌日將花運到沙嶺公墓拜祭。<span class=\"red\">據了解，有民主派區議員近日收到警方消息，指警方高層已下令明天將派出警方國家安全處人員到場監視悼念活動</span>；民主派區議員雖然明白獻花行動或因此有較高風險，但會繼續如常悼念，亦無阻民主派要求政府和港鐵盡快公開全部8.31資料，成立獨立調查委員會徹查警暴的決心。<br />\n<br />\n油尖旺區議會副主席、公民黨余德寶接受《蘋果》查詢時表示，油尖旺區的民主派區議員自今年3月開始，為免巿民到太子站就8.31事件獻花時遭到警方暴力對待，每月的30日或31日，都會自發在太子站外替巿民獻花，直至上月因疫情嚴重才破天荒暫停一次。<br />\n<br />\n余德寶透露，旺角警區指揮官韋能治本月26日曾去信油尖旺區議會主席林健文，「懇請」各油尖旺區區議員停止本月底的所有聚會，但由於疫情近日已回落，故此民主派區議員將緊守2人限聚令，明天傍晚以「兩人一更」方式，恢復上述悼念活動，「8.31事件發生喺太子站，係油尖旺居民同香港人嘅重要歷史，我哋唔可以令呢件事被遺忘」。<br />\n<br />\n余德寶又質疑：「有乜理由政府開咁多個地方做全民檢測就得，我哋跟足『限聚令』舉行活動就唔得？」他指自從民主派區議員今年3月開始代巿民獻花後，旺角出現嚴重衝突的情況，明顯比1、2月時減少。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/XKSK75QF2RANPCDYVQIRWYE6UA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2FXKSK75QF2RANPCDYVQIRWYE6UA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=lPj0fEAhrWGYZLLoA4iNoDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=f9b4b1d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200830%2FXKSK75QF2RANPCDYVQIRWYE6UA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=4c2512ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200830/XKSK75QF2RANPCDYVQIRWYE6UA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"fa327af2973328379226195b8bc306cb85a8a7f0","tid":2181302,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"958e8ae1361d746273e759d0a73161dfdac53878","tid":2181302,"uid":2300,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:27:17.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，又想嚇鳩人唔出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班黑警d 手段真係好撚廢"},{"pid":"4fe56ba4b148babca44852a01948e105870a5084","tid":2181302,"uid":33939,"like":70,"dislike":1,"score":69,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"悼念都要國安，清明重陽國安要請幾多人？"},{"pid":"02bcdd7e172903975db6a0b14e1469ba0e1d3617","tid":2181302,"uid":297949,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9zEwEa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9zEwEa.jpg&h=54fe3334&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a98a3385dd4b26bf3badfeb894a81fd28e95c3e0","tid":2181302,"uid":51271,"like":42,"dislike":2,"score":40,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"另類證明有打死人"},{"pid":"a874958d0d26e5f98e18160322615b9c7d0ab1f1","tid":2181302,"uid":7323,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"出到國安先啦，姐係再一次證明831係發生左大件事。"},{"pid":"97eb65c26c92d8d1f270a15271982832817bd8eb","tid":2181302,"uid":167928,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a874958d0d26e5f98e18160322615b9c7d0ab1f1","tid":2181302,"uid":7323,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:28:41.000Z","msg":"出到國安先啦，姐係再一次證明831係發生左大件事。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:30:27.000Z","msg":"此地無銀三百兩"},{"pid":"2a160b76113b2dc1fe0db2d88c6d28c0dcddd0be","tid":2181302,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T13:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />